properties.CQLScript:
options
	always_reload = true
timeout=300000

schema C = literal: sql {
  entities
    HybridProduct
    RetailProduct
    WholesaleProduct
  foreign_keys
    IsRetail: HybridProduct -> RetailProduct
    IsWholesale: HybridProduct -> WholesaleProduct
  attributes
    nameHP: HybridProduct -> String
    nameRP: RetailProduct -> String
    nameWP: WholesaleProduct -> String
}

schema D = literal : sql {
  entities
    yHybridProduct
    yRetailProduct
    yWholesaleProduct
    yProduct
  foreign_keys
    yIsRetail: yHybridProduct -> yRetailProduct
    yIsWholesale: yHybridProduct -> yWholesaleProduct
    yIsProductRP: yRetailProduct -> yProduct
    yIsProductWP: yWholesaleProduct -> yProduct
  path_equations
    yHybridProduct.yIsRetail.yIsProductRP = yHybridProduct.yIsWholesale.yIsProductWP
  attributes
    ynameHP: yHybridProduct -> String
    ynameRP: yRetailProduct -> String
    ynameWP: yWholesaleProduct -> String
}

mapping F = literal : C -> D {
  entity
    HybridProduct -> yHybridProduct
  foreign_keys
    IsRetail -> yIsRetail
    IsWholesale -> yIsWholesale
  attributes
    nameHP -> ynameHP

  entity
    RetailProduct -> yRetailProduct
  attributes
    nameRP -> ynameRP

  entity
    WholesaleProduct -> yWholesaleProduct
  attributes
    nameWP -> ynameWP
}

instance I = import_csv "/tmp/cql/import" : C {
	HybridProduct -> { HybridProduct -> product_id  IsRetail -> retail_product_id IsWholesale -> wholesale_product_id nameHP -> product_name } 
	RetailProduct -> { RetailProduct -> product_id nameRP -> product_name }
	WholesaleProduct -> { WholesaleProduct -> product_id nameWP -> product_name }
}


instance J = sigma F I

command exportCsvData3 = export_csv_instance J "/tmp/cql/result/out"

options
	always_reload = true
timeout=300000

typeside Ty = literal {
  external_types
    dom -> "java.lang.Object"
  external_parsers
    dom -> "x => x"
}

schema S = literal : Ty {
  entities
    SOrderRaw
  attributes
    SorderId : SOrderRaw -> dom
    ScustName : SOrderRaw -> dom
    SprodName : SOrderRaw -> dom
}

schema T = literal : Ty {
  entities
    TCustomer TProduct TOrder
  attributes
    TcustId : TCustomer -> dom
    TcustName : TCustomer -> dom
    TprodId : TProduct -> dom
    TprodName : TProduct -> dom
    TorderId : TOrder -> dom
    TcustRef : TOrder -> dom
    TprodRef : TOrder -> dom
}

schema ST = literal : Ty {
  imports
    S T
}

schema C = literal: Ty {
	entities
		Customer Product
	attributes
		CustomerName: Customer -> dom
		ProductName: Product -> dom
}

query resultQuery = literal : ST -> C {
entity Customer -> { 
	from 
		y : TCustomer
	attributes
		CustomerName -> TcustName(y)}
	
entity Product -> { 
	from 
		x : TProduct
	attributes
		ProductName -> TprodName(x)}
}

constraints theEDs = literal : ST {
  # Каждая запись о заказе предполагает существование покупателя и продукта
  forall o:TOrder ->
    exists c:TCustomer p:TProduct
    where o.TcustRef = c.TcustId
          o.TprodRef = p.TprodId

  # Каждая запись из OrderRaw приводит к заказу, покупателю и продукту
  forall r:SOrderRaw ->
    exists o:TOrder c:TCustomer p:TProduct
    where r.SorderId = o.TorderId
          c.TcustName = r.ScustName
          p.TprodName = r.SprodName
          o.TcustRef = c.TcustId
          o.TprodRef = p.TprodId

  forall p1:TProduct p2:TProduct
  	where TprodName(p1) = TprodName(p2) -> where p1 = p2

  forall c1:TCustomer c2:TCustomer
  	where TcustName(c1) = TcustName(c2) -> where c1 = c2
}


instance I = import_csv "/tmp/cql/import" : ST {
	SOrderRaw -> { SorderId -> order_id SprodName -> product_name ScustName -> customer_name} 
}


instance J = chase theEDs I
command Check = check theEDs J
instance K = eval resultQuery J
command exportCsvData3 = export_csv_instance K "/tmp/cql/result/out"

options
	always_reload = true
timeout=300000


schema Customer = literal: sql {
	entities 
		PurchaseCustomer
		DemCustomer
	foreign_keys
		customer_id: DemCustomer -> PurchaseCustomer
	attributes
		total_spent : PurchaseCustomer -> Integer
    	age : DemCustomer -> Integer
    	gender : DemCustomer -> String
		customer_id : PurchaseCustomer -> Integer
}



instance CustomerInstance = import_csv "/tmp/cql/import" : Customer {
	PurchaseCustomer -> { PurchaseCustomer -> customer_id  customer_id -> customer_id total_spent -> total_spent} 
	DemCustomer -> { DemCustomer ->  customer_id  customer_id -> customer_id age -> age gender -> gender}
}

schema FullCustomerProfile = literal : sql {
  entities Customer
  attributes
    customer_id : Customer -> Integer
    total_spent : Customer -> Integer
    age : Customer -> Integer
    gender : Customer -> String
}


mapping CustomerToFullProfile = literal : FullCustomerProfile -> Customer {
entity
	Customer -> DemCustomer
	attributes
		customer_id -> customer_id.customer_id
		total_spent -> customer_id.total_spent
		age -> age
		gender -> gender

}


instance FullProfile = delta CustomerToFullProfile CustomerInstance
command exportCsvData3 = export_csv_instance FullProfile "/tmp/cql/result/out"
